Demi Rose, 27, flaunted her hourglass figure in a skin-tight top as she posed for a new series of snaps. In view of her 19.8 million Instagram followers, Demi wore a yellow and white plunging top which barely concealed her ample assets. The model pouted as she filmed herself getting ready. She looked pretty with minimal makeup and her hair styled in loose waves. In the clip, Demi mouthed the lyrics to Days of Wine and Roses by Frank Sinatra.